<b><span size="large">Version 11 (2025-03-01)</span></b>

• Use async file operations to gather wallpaper files and info.
• Add new wallpaper queue sorting options.
    - Random
    - A-Z (Ascending Order)
    - Z-A (Descending Order)
    - Newest First (Date)
    - Oldest First (Date)
• Validate wallpaper queue on startup.
    - Checks if wallpapers were added or removed from the directory on startup.
• Add GNOME 48 support.
• Add Donate page to settings.
• Show notification when Wallpaper Slideshow is updated.
• Cap slide duration minimum to 5 seconds.
• Add Slide Controls to Quick Settings Menu and Settings.
• Add option to re-shuffle slideshow when complete.